{
  "text": "The mechanism underlying the dyspnoea and increased ventilatory response to exercise' [CITATION_1] ' seen in patients with chronic heart failure is unclear' [CITATION_2] '. There is sympathetic activation in chronic heart failure and there are raised levels of circulating nordrenaline'",
